title: Teatergrillen
text:
Teatergrillen

59°20′1″N 18°4′35.2″E﻿ / ﻿59.33361°N 18.076444°E﻿ / 59.33361; 18.076444

Teatergrillen is a Swedish restaurant at Nybrogatan 3 in Stockholm. It was started by Tore Wretman.
